Do some jobs in background service and keep it alive.
The purpose of this project is research.
Please don't use this code in application that published to user. It's a bad way.

Method:
1, run job service and daemon service in seperate process to pretect each other.
2, Use other context to make sure above two services alive.

Usage:
1, Complete BackgroundJob.java
2, Invoke registerTimeTickReceiver(Context) in other context.

Reference:
http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_9f3cecc50101glr4.html
http://blog.csdn.net/boyupeng/article/details/46974855
